01:05:06,080 --> 01:05:09,223
So I might not know your name.

534
01:05:11,240 --> 01:05:13,136
But whatever it is...

535
01:05:14,200 --> 01:05:16,216
I want you to know...

536
01:05:17,520 --> 01:05:19,963
that your dad loves you very much.

537
01:05:33,640 --> 01:05:35,440
From now on,

538
01:05:36,247 --> 01:05:38,216
as you get older,

539
01:05:40,507 --> 01:05:43,440
you'll start to learn more about me...

540
01:05:44,080 --> 01:05:46,320
who I am...

541
01:05:46,320 --> 01:05:48,200
and what I've done.

542
01:05:50,320 --> 01:05:52,120
Because of that,

543
01:05:54,200 --> 01:05:56,010
please...

544
01:05:58,280 --> 01:06:00,556
don't let it weigh on you.

545
01:06:01,720 --> 01:06:03,590
I need you to understand that...

546
01:06:06,480 --> 01:06:08,280
your father is your father,

547
01:06:09,560 --> 01:06:11,360
and you are you.

548
01:06:15,280 --> 01:06:17,210
We're two different people.

549
01:06:19,800 --> 01:06:22,183
