or blame yourself, not even for a second.

551
01:06:32,120 --> 01:06:35,696
If you're watching this video...

552
01:06:43,920 --> 01:06:47,516
it means I'm probably not around anymore.

553
01:06:48,560 --> 01:06:50,360
So,

554
01:06:51,720 --> 01:06:53,520
please...

555
01:06:54,279 --> 01:06:56,856
protect your mom for me, son.

556
01:07:02,080 --> 01:07:03,880
I hope...

557
01:07:08,246 --> 01:07:10,456
you grow up healthy...

558
01:07:13,439 --> 01:07:15,456
and strong.

559
01:07:19,240 --> 01:07:21,430
And no matter what happens,

560
01:07:24,080 --> 01:07:26,320
I want you to know that...

561
01:07:28,400 --> 01:07:30,329
I love you...

562
01:07:31,200 --> 01:07:33,016
and your mother...

563
01:07:34,600 --> 01:07:36,616
more than anything in this world.

564
01:07:45,080 --> 01:07:46,889
Be a good person.
